### 16. Verify stress score is gone → expect 404
GET {{baseUrl}}/stress/scores/latest
Authorization: Bearer {{veteranToken}}

### =====================================================
### DELETE – Stress samples (error paths)
### =====================================================

### 17. No auth token → expect 401
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/stress/samples/me

### =====================================================
### DELETE – Calendar slots (happy path)
### =====================================================

### 18. Delete all slots for therapist → expect 204
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/calendar/slots/me
Authorization: Bearer {{therapistToken}}

### 19. Verify slots are gone → expect empty list
GET {{baseUrl}}/calendar/slots?from=2026-04-01T00:00:00Z&to=2026-04-02T00:00:00Z
Authorization: Bearer {{therapistToken}}

### =====================================================
### DELETE – Calendar slots (error paths)
### =====================================================

### 20. No auth token → expect 401
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/calendar/slots/me

