### =====================================================
### CASCADE – Delete therapist account
### All slots + appointments owned by therapist cascade via trigger
### =====================================================

### 24. Delete therapist account → expect 204
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{therapistToken}}

### 25. Verify therapist slots are gone → expect empty list
GET {{baseUrl}}/calendar/slots?from=2026-05-01T00:00:00Z&to=2026-05-02T00:00:00Z
Authorization: Bearer {{veteranToken}}

### =====================================================
### CASCADE – Delete veteran account
### All mood entries, stress samples/scores, support relations,
### devices, addresses and conversation data cascade via trigger
### =====================================================

### 26. Delete veteran account → expect 204
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{veteranToken}}

### 27. Verify veteran is gone → expect 404
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/{{veteranId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{veteranToken}}

